title: Free! Music! Contest!
description:
On this sampler the winners of the Free! Music! Contest are published. More details can be found (in german) at: <a href="
http://musik.klarmachen-zum-aendern.de/category/allgemein/free_music_contest" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://musik.klarmachen-zum-aendern.de/category/allgemein/free_music_contest</a>

All Tracks are published under a creative commons license. Each license is mentioned in the file's name. The abbreviation in the songs are:

cc-by: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/3.0
cc-by-sa: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/3.0
cc-by-nd: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nd/3.0/
cc-by-nc: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc/3.0
cc-by-nc-sa: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0
cc-by-nc-nd: http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-nd/3.0

If you want to get a physical copy of the sampler, you can order it here: <a href=" http://musik.klarmachen-zum-aendern.de/fmc/sampler" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://musik.klarmachen-zum-aendern.de/fmc/sampler</a>
